Class FallbackDispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sk89q.intake.dispatcher.SimpleDispatcher
      • me.taylorkelly.mywarp.bukkit.util.parametric.FallbackDispatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.sk89q.intake.CommandCallable, com.sk89q.intake.completion.CommandCompleter, com.sk89q.intake.dispatcher.Dispatcher

    public class FallbackDispatcher
extends com.sk89q.intake.dispatcher.SimpleDispatcher
    A custom Dispatcher implementation that, instead of simply throwing an InvalidUsageException if the given arguments do not match any of the registered sub-commands, tries to parse se input against a registered fallback command.
